"    The three marking tools are used to mark points on the drawing screen. Select one of the tools by pressing F6, F7, or F8 (or by moving the cursorover the tool icon and pressing one of the mouse buttons, if you have a ""mouse). To use the tool, locate the cursor where you want a mark, press down a shift key, and release (or press and release one of the mouse buttons). An image of the cursor will be printed to the screen. You can have up to 40 marks ""from each tool on the screen at once.                           (End of Marking Tool Help)"